data.title: Mary Elizabeth “Beth” Brand Cruse (1946
data.meta_description: Mary Elizabeth 'Beth' Brand Cruse 12 April 1946 ~ 16 April 2006  GALENA, Kan. -- Mary E. (Beth) Cruse, age 60, 517 East 6th Street, died at 5 a.m. Sunday, April 16, 2006, at her home following an illness.  Mrs. Cruse was born April 12, 1946, in Galena. Her parents were Charles and Vera (Matthews) Brand.  She had lived...
